---
title: Mushroom Tempura Banh Mi with Pickled Veggies, Carrot Fries, and Sriracha Mayo
description: Is there anything better than the light and airy crunch of something tempura-fried? Seriously, you could coat just about anything in that magical batter and we’d happily chow down. This recipe, though, happens to be extra special. Mighty mushrooms turn addictively crispy on the outside and juicy on the inside thanks to the easy technique. They’re then piled into crusty bread along with pickled cucumber and jalapeño, grated carrot, cilantro leaves, and sriracha mayo. On the side, there’s sweet and tender carrot fries. What are you waiting for?!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mushroom-tempura-banh-mi-sandwiches-96cdc7d5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/mushroom-tempura-banh-mi-sandwiches-5db8973b0765962fe312b543-79fe78a4.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/mushroom-tempura-banh-mi-sandwiches-5db8973b0765962fe312b543
course: main course
time required: 45m
nutrition:
  calories: 820 kcal
  fat: 33 g
  saturated fat: 6 g
  carbohydrates: 95 g
